36
00:04:37,011 --> 00:04:38,311
- Get out!

37
00:04:38,445 --> 00:04:39,479
- All we could really
do is get outta the way.

38
00:04:39,614 --> 00:04:40,447
- No one's takin' me to the hospital.

39
00:04:40,581 --> 00:04:41,949
- You gotta calm down!

40
00:04:42,083 --> 00:04:43,416
Please!

41
00:04:43,551 --> 00:04:44,886
- Get outta here!

42
00:04:45,019 --> 00:04:45,920
Go!

43
00:04:47,889 --> 00:04:50,992
- I started at a
young age, a very young age.

44
00:04:52,860 --> 00:04:54,929
Come to the woods and bringin'
back somethin' you could eat.

45
00:04:56,664 --> 00:05:00,535
Squirrel, ducks, quail,
doves, whatever was there.

46
00:05:01,569 --> 00:05:03,004
The woods became my home.

47
00:05:04,605 --> 00:05:07,041
Sometimes I would just
sit there for hours,

48
00:05:07,175 --> 00:05:08,242
listen to the woods.

49
00:05:09,043 --> 00:05:12,747
They would talk and I
would try and talk back.

50
00:05:17,450 --> 00:05:18,886
I could get lost in them.

51
00:05:20,420 --> 00:05:22,056
They were my refuge.

52
00:05:24,892 --> 00:05:30,131
