No, no!
- Phil!

55
00:06:19,981 --> 00:06:21,349
They're takin' her away again!
- You can't make me!

56
00:06:21,481 --> 00:06:23,885
You can't make me, you can't!

57
00:06:24,018 --> 00:06:25,152
No!

58
00:06:25,286 --> 00:06:26,220
Phil!

59
00:06:26,354 --> 00:06:27,288
Phil, don't let 'em take me!

60
00:06:27,420 --> 00:06:28,990
- She ain't done nothin' wrong!

61
00:06:29,123 --> 00:06:31,391
- Judy, Judy!

62
00:06:31,525 --> 00:06:33,094
Phil, Phil, Phil!

63
00:06:35,196 --> 00:06:38,266
- Mom!

64
00:06:38,398 --> 00:06:39,233
- Phil!

65
