114
00:09:00,674 --> 00:09:01,876
- Thanks, Daddy.

115
00:09:05,179 --> 00:09:07,715
- Kay wasn't like the other kids.

116
00:09:07,848 --> 00:09:09,216
They judged us.

117
00:09:10,117 --> 00:09:11,018
