so don't go cheatin' out on me again.

197
00:12:43,598 --> 00:12:45,065
- Okay.

198
00:12:45,199 --> 00:12:47,234
- Fries are for skinny bones.

199
00:12:50,771 --> 00:12:51,805
- In those days,

200
