There's just a lot goin' on.

245
00:14:46,855 --> 00:14:49,758
- Hey, whoa, it's okay.

246
00:14:49,890 --> 00:14:51,526
We can figure it out together.

247
00:14:52,594 --> 00:14:53,460
- No, no, all right?

248
00:14:53,595 --> 00:14:54,863
You shouldn't...

249
00:14:54,995 --> 00:14:56,463
No, you're not gonna have
to deal with any of this.

250
00:14:56,598 --> 00:14:58,098
- Hey, who needs another
muffy at Fertitta's?

251
00:14:58,232 --> 00:14:59,601
I've got an idea.

252
00:15:02,903 --> 00:15:04,539
- Thank you again for bringin' all this.

253
00:15:04,672 --> 00:15:06,473
- Well, just because my
parents own a grocery store

254
00:15:06,608 --> 00:15:08,610
