to cook anything in it.

255
00:15:08,743 --> 00:15:10,812
- Well, honey, that I can teach.

256
00:15:10,944 --> 00:15:12,212
Always start with some butter here.

257
00:15:12,346 --> 00:15:14,014
- baby, okay?

258
00:15:14,148 --> 00:15:15,683
Give us a snack, all right?

259
00:15:15,817 --> 00:15:16,984
No one-
- Coca-Cola?

